title: Who Would You Fuck?
description:
Written by John Sartori
Starring Ryan Farrell, Bardia Salimi, Keith Kingbay, Audrey Stanfield

Performed at The Upright Citizen's Brigade Theater as part of Maude Night (3/9/15).
Directed by: Geoff Garlock
Shot by: Charlie Purdom
